{"tid":1126829,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"暗星與盲粉","createTime":"2019-04-26T15:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T05:09:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee917e0013ca421a40c680392ddf5beb820e207d","tid":1126829,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190426/20664096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F20664096&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjqwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=b9777856\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F20664096&h=2a4b6c43\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190426/20664096</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暗星與盲粉 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190426/large/e8804a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190426%2Flarge%2Fe8804a.jpg&h=9c109f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n日前上海虹橋機場人山人海，場面堪比春運，熱情的粉絲把航站樓自動行人道的玻璃也逼爆了，碎片散落一地，十分危險。<br />\n<br />\n原來大量年輕男女粉絲，見網上流傳名單，當日飛抵上海或由上海出發的「明星」有十多位，他們蜂擁而至，接（送）機、拍攝、舉牌、叫喊&hellip;&hellip;為明星造勢，有些早上10點已來，擠得水洩不通，等不到自己偶像，反而製造了意外。<br />\n<br />\n所謂粉絲，明星的fans，理智的少，腦殘的多──腦殘粉、死忠粉、顏粉、屏幕粉、手機粉、前綫粉、私生粉、路人粉、cp粉、親媽粉、後媽粉、團粉、狂粉&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但好些是盲頭烏蠅，資訊不清楚，人圍我又圍，人衝我又衝，苦等苦候得個吉，統統是「盲粉」──<br />\n<br />\n好了，究竟追的什麼明星呀？有名單的：──曾&times;晞、王&times;凱、魏&times;勛、蘇&times;琪、王&times;博、卜&times;、靈&times;、鄧&times;元、黃&times;昊&hellip;&hellip;聽過嗎？Sorry，一個也不認識，都不知是誰？當然，全是大陸星，不能以網絡散布假新聞、假消息視之，也不能說是違反「商品說明條例」之誤導假貨，只是各人要求不同標準各異。我們比較勢利。<br />\n<br />\n為了暗星而瘋狂的盲粉，真是天造地設，相得益彰。  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n台灣政治講銀紙 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n六和塔 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"97d2c6be62113ade2c51259471d45d291e35c6ec","tid":1126829,"uid":244361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"香港都有mirror<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfa8e074fc973bd8a3499f6208dc2fd9c4cd585","tid":1126829,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"王&times;凱係咪王俊凱?"},{"pid":"eee28801622b04a3af5992156004f17f209c1c30","tid":1126829,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T23:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4de1e0c01850143f53d11c505ada18e0d4deb50c","tid":1126829,"uid":91238,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"97d2c6be62113ade2c51259471d45d291e35c6ec","tid":1126829,"uid":244361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"香港都有mirror<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:50:45.000Z","msg":"請成埋打手上Facebook推，九成Fans都係卡通Icon留咩柒「姜B❤️」"},{"pid":"edeb21907a5b377e81abf41a28385e1dd86cd198","tid":1126829,"uid":137694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cdfa8e074fc973bd8a3499f6208dc2fd9c4cd585","tid":1126829,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"王&times;凱係咪王俊凱?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:28:53.000Z","msg":"佢都暗星？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8637b9edcac68497df6b2a62007670df6cad896","tid":1126829,"uid":122985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"關暗唔暗星咩事 <br />\n個人種係咁就係咁 追星都係無秩序"},{"pid":"3c1d04fc08743deb35983836b5d10896e23c1692","tid":1126829,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:09:22.000